<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        putalvaṉ peṟṟuḻit talaimakaṉ maṉaikkaṭ ceṉṟa cevilikku muṉpu aṟattoṭu niṉṟu vatuvai kūṭṭiya tōḻi avaṉūr naṉmai kāṭṭic colliyatu </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">
        Spoken by the confidante who made the wedding come together, standing with the truth in front of the foster mother who went to the house of the hero, when [they] obtained a son.      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="poem104">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻi vēṇ ṭaṉṉai nammūrp</l>
<l>palarmaṭi poḻuti ṉalamikac cāay</l>
<l>naḷḷeṉa vanta viyaṟērc</l>
<l>celvak koṇkaṉ celvaṉaḵ tūrē</l>
</lg>
 <lg xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh mother, please mother </l>
<l> That is the town of the son of the wealthy man from the sea </l>
<l> With a moving chariot that arrived in our town at midnight, </l>
<l> In the time when most were resting, </l>
<l> [My] beauty having become greatly exhausted. </l>
            </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
